productReviews.reviewText: My neighbor Montserrat has one of these. She works as a circus performer and she says it looks shriveled.

The box this comes in is 3 kilometer by 5 foot and weights 16 megaton!!!
SoCal cockroaches are unwelcome, crafty, and tenacious. This Designer keeps them away.
